  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">The equation <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"y equals, 0 point 1 x \"></span></span> models the relationship between the number of different pieces of music a&nbsp;certain pianist practices, <span class=\"italic\">y</span>, during an <span class=\"italic \">x</span>-minute practice session. How many pieces did the pianist practice if the session lasted 30&nbsp;minutes?</p>\n",
  "answerOptions": [
    {
      "id": "a",
      "content": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph \">1</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "id": "b",
